    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "img_branch_text",
      "x": 320,
      "y": 158,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 130,
      "text": "Image Branch (Cam2BEV)\n\nSwinT-Tiny [Backbone, 预训练]\n  → FPN 多尺度融合\n  → LSS 深度估计 (D=89 bins)\n  → BEV Pool [CUDA 加速]\n  → ProjectionHead\n→ (B, 128, 100, 100)",
      "originalText": "Image Branch (Cam2BEV)\n\nSwinT-Tiny [Backbone, 预训练]\n  → FPN 多尺度融合\n  → LSS 深度估计 (D=89 bins)\n  → BEV Pool [CUDA 加速]\n  → ProjectionHead\n→ (B, 128, 100, 100)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#ffffff",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
