    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "loss_block_text",
      "x": 1030,
      "y": 313,
      "width": 330,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "realworld_loss (多项加权)\n\n基础损失:\n  translation_loss  SmoothL1    w=1.0\n  rotation_loss     四元数距离    w=0.5\n  PC_reproj_loss    3D重投影     w=0.5\n  quat_norm_loss    单位约束     w=0.5\n\n高级损失 (V11 新增):\n  AdaptiveAxisRotationLoss      w=0.3\n    Roll×3.0 + Pitch×1.5 + Yaw×1.0\n    + tail penalty (top-10% × 2.0)\n    → 解决 Roll 轴收敛困难问题",
      "originalText": "realworld_loss (多项加权)\n\n基础损失:\n  translation_loss  SmoothL1    w=1.0\n  rotation_loss     四元数距离    w=0.5\n  PC_reproj_loss    3D重投影     w=0.5\n  quat_norm_loss    单位约束     w=0.5\n\n高级损失 (V11 新增):\n  AdaptiveAxisRotationLoss      w=0.3\n    Roll×3.0 + Pitch×1.5 + Yaw×1.0\n    + tail penalty (top-10% × 2.0)\n    → 解决 Roll 轴收敛困难问题",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
