    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "optim_block_text",
      "x": 690,
      "y": 553,
      "width": 670,
      "height": 78,
      "text": "1. Image Branch 对 init_T 敏感 → 大扰动下 BEV 投影偏移严重 → 可探索迭代精化策略\n2. ConvFuser 仅用 1×1 Conv → 可尝试 cross-attention 或 deformable fusion 增强跨模态交互\n3. 全局 mean pool 丢失空间信息 → 可探索 spatial attention 或 multi-scale pooling\n4. Tail penalty 仅作用于 axis loss → 可扩展到 translation loss 处理长尾分布\n5. backbone_lr_scale=0.1 冻结大部分 backbone → 可尝试渐进解冻 (progressive unfreezing)",
      "originalText": "1. Image Branch 对 init_T 敏感 → 大扰动下 BEV 投影偏移严重 → 可探索迭代精化策略\n2. ConvFuser 仅用 1×1 Conv → 可尝试 cross-attention 或 deformable fusion 增强跨模态交互\n3. 全局 mean pool 丢失空间信息 → 可探索 spatial attention 或 multi-scale pooling\n4. Tail penalty 仅作用于 axis loss → 可扩展到 translation loss 处理长尾分布\n5. backbone_lr_scale=0.1 冻结大部分 backbone → 可尝试渐进解冻 (progressive unfreezing)",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
