    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "data_pipeline_text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 718,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 175,
      "text": "Dataset & DataLoader\n\nKittiDataset / CustomDataset → PreprocessedDataset 包装 → collate_fn 批处理\n\ncollate_fn 关键步骤:\n  1. crop_and_resize(img) → 统一尺寸\n  2. intrinsic 按 resize 比例缩放 fx,fy,cx,cy\n  3. PC padding → (max_N, 3) + mask tensor\n  4. ego_filter: |x|>3 & |y|>3 过滤自车点\n  5. range_filter: xbound/ybound/zbound 裁剪\n\nCustomDataset 特性: 支持预缩放图像 image_2_{W}x{H}/, validate_data_utilization()",
      "originalText": "Dataset & DataLoader\n\nKittiDataset / CustomDataset → PreprocessedDataset 包装 → collate_fn 批处理\n\ncollate_fn 关键步骤:\n  1. crop_and_resize(img) → 统一尺寸\n  2. intrinsic 按 resize 比例缩放 fx,fy,cx,cy\n  3. PC padding → (max_N, 3) + mask tensor\n  4. ego_filter: |x|>3 & |y|>3 过滤自车点\n  5. range_filter: xbound/ybound/zbound 裁剪\n\nCustomDataset 特性: 支持预缩放图像 image_2_{W}x{H}/, validate_data_utilization()",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
