    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "augmentation_text",
      "x": 690,
      "y": 718,
      "width": 670,
      "height": 188,
      "text": "Data Augmentation & Perturbation\n\n标定扰动 (init_T 生成):\n  分布: uniform / truncated_normal (推荐)\n  per_axis_prob: 每轴独立扰动概率 | per_axis_weights: [roll, pitch, yaw]\n  范围: ±5°~10° rotation, ±0.1~0.5m translation\n\n数据增强 (可选):\n  color_jitter — brightness/contrast/saturation ×0.3\n  pc_jitter — Gaussian noise on xyz (sigma in meters)\n  pc_dropout — 随机丢弃部分点云\n\n设计: truncated_normal 更符合真实标定偏差分布, 效果显著优于 uniform",
      "originalText": "Data Augmentation & Perturbation\n\n标定扰动 (init_T 生成):\n  分布: uniform / truncated_normal (推荐)\n  per_axis_prob: 每轴独立扰动概率 | per_axis_weights: [roll, pitch, yaw]\n  范围: ±5°~10° rotation, ±0.1~0.5m translation\n\n数据增强 (可选):\n  color_jitter — brightness/contrast/saturation ×0.3\n  pc_jitter — Gaussian noise on xyz (sigma in meters)\n  pc_dropout — 随机丢弃部分点云\n\n设计: truncated_normal 更符合真实标定偏差分布, 效果显著优于 uniform",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
