    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "eval_text",
      "x": 730,
      "y": 948,
      "width": 630,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "evaluate_checkpoint.py — 三种模式: eval | compare | multi_eval\n  输出: extrinsics_and_errors.txt + 可视化投影图 + Feishu 报告\n\nevaluate_extrinsics.py — SE(3) → 6-DoF 误差 (roll/pitch/yaw + fwd/lat/ht)\nrun_generalization_eval.py — config 驱动多模型跨数据集泛化测试\ninference_kitti.py — KITTI 推理 + TensorBoard 可视化\n\n误差度量: LiDAR 坐标系下物理意义明确的旋转/平移分解",
      "originalText": "evaluate_checkpoint.py — 三种模式: eval | compare | multi_eval\n  输出: extrinsics_and_errors.txt + 可视化投影图 + Feishu 报告\n\nevaluate_extrinsics.py — SE(3) → 6-DoF 误差 (roll/pitch/yaw + fwd/lat/ht)\nrun_generalization_eval.py — config 驱动多模型跨数据集泛化测试\ninference_kitti.py — KITTI 推理 + TensorBoard 可视化\n\n误差度量: LiDAR 坐标系下物理意义明确的旋转/平移分解",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
