    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ckpt_text",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 1258,
      "width": 240,
      "height": 133,
      "text": "Checkpoint 管理\n\nckpt_{epoch}.pth — 周期保存\nckpt_best_val.pth — 最优验证\n\n内容: model/optimizer state,\n  epoch errors, best metrics,\n  args, 源码快照\n→ training_summary.md",
      "originalText": "Checkpoint 管理\n\nckpt_{epoch}.pth — 周期保存\nckpt_best_val.pth — 最优验证\n\n内容: model/optimizer state,\n  epoch errors, best metrics,\n  args, 源码快照\n→ training_summary.md",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
