    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "logging_text",
      "x": 320,
      "y": 1258,
      "width": 248,
      "height": 133,
      "text": "Logging 系统\n\ntprint() — 带时间戳 → train.log\n_StderrTee — stderr → train.log\ncapture_prints() — DDP worker 静默\n\nTensorBoard:\n  SummaryWriter (scalars+images)\n  batch_train.sh 管理生命周期",
      "originalText": "Logging 系统\n\ntprint() — 带时间戳 → train.log\n_StderrTee — stderr → train.log\ncapture_prints() — DDP worker 静默\n\nTensorBoard:\n  SummaryWriter (scalars+images)\n  batch_train.sh 管理生命周期",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
