      "y": 1258,
      "width": 282,
      "height": 147,
      "text": "Config 系统\n\nYAML: global + defaults + experiments\n  defaults.env: BEV_ZBOUND_STEP...\n  defaults.params: lr, epochs...\n  experiments[]: per-exp overrides\n\n数据集映射:\n  B26A → b26a1_1_training_data\n  all → all_training_data",
